7\tThis app provides educational and self-help tools, not medical advice. Crisis/safety 
resources must be shown for severe withdrawal, suicidal ideation, or medical 
emergencies.\n     8\t\n     9\t## Science-based approaches to include\n    10\t1) CBT 
basics (Cognitive Behavioral Therapy): trigger -> thought -> craving -> action mapping; 
reframe prompts.\n    11\t2) Motivational Interviewing (MI) style reflections: values 
clarification, reasons to quit, confidence scaling (0-10).\n    12\t3) Implementation 
intentions: "If X happens, then I will do Y."\n    13\t4) Urge surfing: timed craving 
timer + breathing / grounding exercises.\n    14\t5) Habit substitution: replacement 
